properties.name: Whakahoro Camping Ground
properties.memory: Playing rummikub with Ben and Soph

properties.name: Whakapapa Scenic Reserve
properties.memory: Wild camping, Mario and Saskia, Kota and Naru were there, I had a dip in the river, Becky and Louisa suprised me by appearing NOBO

properties.name: Tongariro Holiday Park
properties.memory: Met Nicky here. Alaskan Mike appeared after shaving his beard off. Had a good chat with Italian Lea

properties.name: Pureora Cabins
properties.memory: Made pancakes with Saskia for Kath, Liz and Jackie! Mario appeared. I carved spoons in my own cabin until Patrick joined on night 2

properties.name: Waitomo Top 10 Holiday Park
properties.memory: Ran into Saskia after a long while. Met Alaskan Mike, Emily and Lizzie here. Had a nice burger over the road and saw the glow worms

properties.name: Kaniwhaniwha Campsite
properties.memory: Celebrated my birthday here with the golden gang. They decorated the camp and brought me a beer and cake :))

properties.name: The Village Cafe
properties.memory: We camped here in the cafe grounds. Bar over the road had a cover band (classic metal/rock but can't remember who) - actually pretty good just loud and late!

properties.name: Mercer Motel
properties.memory: Weird place to camp up between a couple of highways. Reunited with Jon and Vivienne here

properties.name: Pakiri Beach Holiday Park
properties.memory: A nice holiday park, I got here first after storming ahead from the group

properties.name: Uretiti Beach DOC Campsite
properties.memory: Beautiful campsite, Katie and I stargazed here

properties.name: Ahipara Holiday Park
properties.memory: Got fish and chips down the road from this place after our first ever (short) hitch. Had a couple of beers in the cabin and felt good

properties.name: Hone Heke Lodge
properties.memory: Wonderful, friendly, helpful people, cannot fault them

properties.name: Twilight Beach Campsite
properties.memory: The first camp! All of us were trying to work out what we were doing. Wonderful sunset
